### File Format Quick Reference

**GFF-based Templates** (use `CSharpKOTOR.Formats.GFF`):
- `UTC` - Creature template
- `UTP` - Placeable template  
- `UTD` - Door template
- `UTT` - Trigger template
- `UTW` - Waypoint template
- `UTS` - Sound template
- `UTE` - Encounter template
- `UTI` - Item template
- `DLG` - Dialogue tree
- `ARE` - Area properties
- `GIT` - Instance list
- `IFO` - Module info

**ASCII Formats**:
- `LYT` - Room layout (rooms, doorhooks, tracks)
- `VIS` - Visibility graph (room-to-room)
- `TXI` - Texture properties
- `2DA` - Data tables

**Binary Formats**:
- `MDL/MDX` - Models and vertex data
- `TPC` - Compressed textures (DXT)
- `BWM` - Walkmesh (WOK/PWK/DWK)
- `NCS` - Compiled scripts
- `LIP` - Lipsync keyframes
- `WAV` - Audio